skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: palo alto vegan
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Palo Alto. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Palo Alto Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Palo Alto Vegan for a fact."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
